\begin{thm}
Let $f\in C\left([ 0,1]^{2} \right)$, then we have
\begin{eqnarray*}
\left\|B^{(p_{1},q_{1}),(p_{2},q_{2})}_{n,m}\left(f;x,y\right)-f(x,y)\right\|_{C\left([
0,1]^{2} \right)}\leq2M\left(f;\delta_{n,m}(x,y)/2 \right),
